{"tid":1794572,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"行山新手意見收集","createTime":"2019-12-23T08:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-23T10:41:42.000Z","uid":252540,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"993469101093c25db105554ef11fe350553cd90c","tid":1794572,"uid":252540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:15:53.000Z","msg":"聖誕想獨自行山 諗住行城門水塘 我未行過山 自問體力應該可以完成到<br />\n但擔心會唔會有蕩失路/意外 雖然睇人地話只要右手邊係水塘就冇行錯路<br />\n始終冇經驗都有小小驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋小弟身材較瘦同睇落易恰 睇新聞有人遇到打劫 我一定係呢堆賊人既目標<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想問下各位點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會唔會真係第一次行山/睇落易恰搵人陪會好D？但我身邊冇朋友鍾意行山<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b233bfa4023992581caaafb88405ac14e06bd40d","tid":1794572,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:19:01.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[我終於搵到FC撚嘅歸屬地] 已經整好左個搜尋器，而家要大家俾意見想要有咩類別<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1794463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1794463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"9f9934e7277d718ccf73141598140aa6837dedfe","tid":1794572,"uid":252540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:19:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"df2fa605c4e9c086e1aa04401580b9153173c26d","tid":1794572,"uid":49094,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:20:02.000Z","msg":"行城門一定要帶膠袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91fa8c0b4c6044ae428d1dad2d0cd237c5d51aeb","tid":1794572,"uid":102594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-23T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"攰就返轉頭<br />\n遲去驚夜山就買枝行山電筒<br />\n其實閑日都好多鬼佬同中年一個行<br />\n冇乜危險"},{"pid":"99418da4a69a490a037d9abcf727339b25a69070","tid":1794572,"uid":38204,"like":0,"d